Also they sell fish. Mostly whole fish. They also have a good assortment of vegetables. On my picture you will see the bitter veggies. Their spice level is fairly normal. But I did not like their bitter flavor, I think it does not combine well with the spice.
review 2: Nice, clean, comfort, cheap, bigger parking lot. This restaurant give you an ordinary indonesia home serving. So basically this restaurant serves home cooking food. It's good for someone that want to try Indonesia home cooking food, feels like your indonesian
